# Project Architecture

## Tech stack

React 19 · Vite 6 · TypeScript · Tailwind CSS v4 · react-router v7 · i18next · Radix UI · recharts · motion · vite-plugin-pwa · Supabase (optional) · Vercel

## Directory map

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Public pages | `src/pages/` |
| Admin pages | `src/pages/Admin*.tsx` |
| Shared UI | `src/components/ui/core.tsx` |
| Layout | `src/components/layout/` |
| Admin UI | `src/components/admin/` |
| Domain types | `src/types/domain.ts` |
| Seed data | `src/data/` (re-exported via `src/data.ts`) |
| App state | `src/contexts/DataContext.tsx` → `useAppStore()` |
| Auth | `src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx` |
| i18n | `src/i18n/` + `src/locales/{vi,en}/` |
| Nav config | `src/config/nav.ts` |
| Site/SEO config | `src/config/site.ts` |
| Hooks | `src/hooks/` |
| Utils | `src/lib/` |

## Conventions

- Path alias: `@/` → `src/`
- Class merging: `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`
- Default locale: `vi` (English secondary)

## Rule index

| Topic | Rule file |
|-------|-----------|
| Colors, typography, surfaces | `design-system.mdc` |
| Shared components, layouts | `components.mdc` |
| TypeScript & React patterns | `typescript-react.mdc` |
| Translations | `i18n.mdc` |
| Data & persistence | `data-layer.mdc` |
| Routes & navigation | `routing-navigation.mdc` |
| Performance | `performance.mdc` |
| Accessibility | `accessibility.mdc` |
| SEO & PWA | `seo-and-pwa.mdc` |
| Media uploads (Cloudinary) | `media-upload.mdc` |
| Supabase + Vercel deploy | `supabase-vercel.mdc` |

